Package: adRutils
Title: Utility Functions for Data Analysis Workflows
Version: 2.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Ana", "Boeriu",
           email = "ana.boeriu@ucsf.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Utility functions supporting tidy data analysis workflows,
    including input validation, data cleaning, longitudinal coalescing,
    regression model batching, coefficient extraction, and random-effects
    meta-analysis. Designed to reduce boilerplate in research scripts and
    to work alongside domain-specific packages.
